# TRAK — Product Requirements Document (PRD)
### Version 2.0 · March 2026

---

![TRAK Hero](trak_hero_mockup_1772867147562.png)

---

## 1. Product Overview

**TRAK** is a unified health accountability platform that fuses **Nutrition Tracking**, **Habit Building**, **Fitness Logging**, and **Social Accountability (Squads)** into a single, gamified mobile-first experience. It leverages behavioral psychology — streaks, social proof, and variable reward mechanics — to convert intention into lasting behavior change.

> **Mission:** Make consistency the product, not perfection.

---

