## 3. Feature Modules

### 3.1 🥗 Nutrition Engine

| Feature | Description | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| **Calorie Dashboard** | Circular gauge showing daily intake vs target | ✅ Live |
| **Macro Pie Chart** | Protein / Carbs / Fat breakdown with labeled percentages | ✅ Live |
| **Micronutrient Web** | Radar chart showing RDA coverage for 7+ micronutrients | ✅ Live |
| **AI Meal Scan** | Camera → GPT-4o Vision → auto-parsed nutrients (Trak+ only) | ✅ Live |
| **Manual Meal Entry** | Text-based meal logging with nutrient auto-lookup | ✅ Live |
| **Nutrition Trends** | 7-day / 28-day calorie and macro trend charts | ✅ Live |

**Data Model:** `nutrition_entries` table with `user_id`, `meal_name`, `calories`, `protein`, `carbs`, `fat`, `micros (JSONB)`, `created_at`

---

### 3.2 ✅ Habits Engine

| Feature | Description | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| **Daily Habit Grid** | Toggle-based checklist of active habits | ✅ Live |
| **Add/Edit Habits** | Modal to create custom habits with icons and frequency | ✅ Live |
| **Streak Badges** | Visual badges showing current streak per habit | ✅ Live |
| **Perfect Day Detection** | Awards "Perfect Day" when all active habits are completed | ✅ Live |
| **Habit Trends** | Heatmap calendar and completion rate charts | ✅ Live |

**Data Model:** `habits` (definitions), `habit_completions` (daily toggles), `habit_streaks` (current + best streak per habit)

---

### 3.3 🏋️ Fitness Engine

| Feature | Description | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| **Workout Logger** | Log activity type, duration, calories burned | ✅ Live |
| **MET Calculator** | Auto-calculates calories from activity + duration using MET values | ✅ Live |
| **Fitness Trends** | Weekly workout frequency and calorie burn charts | ✅ Live |

**Data Model:** `workouts` table with `user_id`, `activity`, `duration_minutes`, `calories_burned`, `created_at`

**Utility:** [METs.ts](file:///c:/Users/samcu/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/trak/src/utils/METs.ts) — 50+ activity MET lookup table for calorie estimation

---

### 3.4 👥 Squads (Multiplayer Engine)

| Feature | Description | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| **Create Squad** | Deploy a private squad with auto-generated 6-char join code | ✅ Live |
| **Join Squad** | OTP-style 6-box code input with auto-focus and paste support | ✅ Live |
| **Activity Feed** | Real-time Supabase listener showing squad member actions | ✅ Live |
| **Emoji Reactions** | 🔥💪🙌👀 with Canvas Confetti micro-explosions and haptic feedback | ✅ Live |
| **Holographic Leaderboard** | Gold/Silver/Bronze podium with weekly season reset | ✅ Live |
| **Tiered Milestone Cards** | Streak milestones (3/5/10/21/30/50/100) as celebration banners | ✅ Live |
| **Multi-Squad Toggle** | Horizontal pill switcher (2 basic / 5 Trak+) | ✅ Live |
| **Share Invite** | Web Share API → WhatsApp/iMessage with clipboard fallback | ✅ Live |
| **Achievement Popup** | Tappable profile cards → glassmorphic detail modal | ✅ Live |

**Scoring System:**

| Action | Points |
|--------|--------|
| ✅ Habit Completion | +5 |
| ⭐ Perfect Habit Day | +25 |
| 🎯 Calorie Target Hit | +50 |
| 🏋️ Workout Logged | +50 |
| 🔱 Trifecta Bonus (all 3 pillars) | +10 |
| 🔥 Reaction Given | +2 |

