## 4. User Flow Map

```mermaid
journey
    title New User Onboarding
    section Discovery
      Land on marketing page: 5: User
      Sign up with email/social: 4: User
    section Calibration
      Enter biometrics (age, weight, height): 3: User
      Set daily calorie target: 4: User
      Select initial habits: 4: User
      Loading/calibration animation: 5: System
    section Daily Loop
      Morning Debrief shows yesterday's recap: 5: System
      Log meals via scan or manual entry: 4: User
      Check off daily habits: 5: User
      Log a workout: 3: User
      Check squad feed and react: 5: User
      Review trends before bed: 3: User
```

---

## 5. Technical Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| **Frontend** | Next.js 15 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion |
| **Backend** | Supabase (Auth, Postgres, Realtime, RPC) |
| **AI** | OpenAI GPT-4o Vision (meal scanning) |
| **Hosting** | Vercel (Edge Functions + CDN) |
| **Gamification** | canvas-confetti, custom framer-motion choreography |
| **PWA** | Mobile-first responsive, installable as home screen app |

---

## 6. Monetization: Trak Free vs Trak+

| Feature | Free | Trak+ ($4.99/mo) |
|---------|------|-------------------|
| Nutrition tracking | ✅ | ✅ |
| Habits | 5 max | Unlimited |
| Fitness logging | ✅ | ✅ |
| AI Meal Scan | ❌ | ✅ |
| Squads | 2 max | 5 max |
| Trends | 7-day | 28-day |
| Shake Builder | ❌ | ✅ |
| Badge card tier | Standard | Gold border + Crown |

---

## 7. Badge Tier System

| Threshold | Icon | Title | Card Treatment |
|-----------|------|-------|----------------|
| 0 days | — | Unranked | Default border |
| 3+ days | 🌱 | Getting Started | Green tint |
| 5+ days | 🔥 | Momentum | Orange glow |
| 10+ days | ⚡ | Double Digits | Blue aura |
| 21+ days | 💪 | Habit Formed | Purple shimmer |
| 30+ days | 🎯 | Monthly Master | Emerald radiance |
| 50+ days | 💎 | Elite | Gold border |
| 100+ days | 👑 | Legendary | Full gold + crown |

