## 8. Database Schema (Key Tables)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USERS ||--o{ NUTRITION_ENTRIES : logs
    USERS ||--o{ HABITS : creates
    USERS ||--o{ HABIT_COMPLETIONS : completes
    USERS ||--o{ HABIT_STREAKS : tracks
    USERS ||--o{ WORKOUTS : logs
    USERS ||--o{ SQUAD_MEMBERS : joins
    SQUADS ||--o{ SQUAD_MEMBERS : contains
    SQUADS ||--o{ SQUAD_FEED : generates
    SQUAD_FEED ||--o{ SQUAD_REACTIONS : receives

    USERS {
        uuid id PK
        text name
        int member_number
        bool is_trak_plus
        timestamp created_at
    }
    SQUADS {
        uuid id PK
        text name
        text join_code
        text timezone
        uuid created_by FK
    }
    SQUAD_FEED {
        uuid id PK
        uuid squad_id FK
        uuid user_id FK
        text event_type
        jsonb metadata
        timestamp created_at
    }
